      "text": "**🐦 GenAI Control Plane Architecture (Layered Approach)**\n\n**HOOK:**\nStop building monolithic AI systems! 🛑 The secret to scalable GenAI is a Layered Control Plane architecture. Learn how to turn raw data into intelligent action. 👇\n\n**Tweet 1:**\n1/8 🧵 What is GenAI Control Plane Architecture (Layered Approach) and why should you care? It’s the blueprint for building AI systems that are safe, scalable, and smart. Let's dive\n\n*…8 tweets…*\n\n**Last:**\n8/8 Summary: 3 Key Takeaways:\n1. Separate the workflow (Ingest, Enrich, Reason, Orchestrate).\n2. Safety first: Separation prevents cascading\n\n**CTA:**\nMastering system architecture is the difference between a broken AI and a production-ready powerhouse. Follow for more deep-dive tech breakd",
