      "id": "lv-71700e36-eli5",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**🍼 ELI5**\n**GenAI-Driven Observability and Incident Response Control Plane**\n\nImagine a smart robot watching a toy factory. It doesn't just see smoke; it knows exactly which machine is broken and tells the repair crew exactly how to fix it. This smart system helps keep everything running perfectly and stops big messes before they start.",
      "x": 1000,
      "y": -1300,
