    },
    {
      "id": "st-b8a571f7-3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 4**\n\nStep 4: Grasp the mechanism — Trace how AIOps uses structured data (logs/metrics) for detection, contrasting this with how GenAI uses unstructured data (tickets/docs) for synthesis.",
