      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "st-b8a571f7-4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 5**\n\nStep 5: Study the transition — Explore the shift from narrow statistical modeling (AIOps) to holistic contextual reasoning (GenAI).",
