      "height": 200,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "st-493226f9-0",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 1**\n\nStep 1: Understand the problem — what pain does GenAI Control Plane Architecture (Layered Approach) solve and why did it exist?",
      "x": 110,
      "y": 2490,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "st-493226f9-1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 2**\n\nStep 2: Learn the vocabulary — define the 3-5 key terms you will encounter (e.g., telemetry, orchestration, reasoning, decoupling, latency).",
