    },
    {
      "id": "st-493226f9-6",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 7**\n\nStep 7: Learn what can go wrong — identify failure modes specific to distributed systems (e.g., data lineage breaks, state persistence errors, asynchronous feedback loops) and how to diagnose them.",
      "x": 1970,
