    },
    {
      "id": "st-dcfaa698-4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 5**\n\nStep 5: Identify the parts — what are the components and how do they interact (LLM, data embedding/vector DB, feature engineering, uncertainty modeling)?",
