      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "st-dcfaa698-6",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 7**\n\nStep 7: Learn what can go wrong — failure modes and how to diagnose them (temporal misalignment, sensor drift, hallucination of causal links).",
