    },
    {
      "id": "st-6c1957f1-2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Step 3**\n\nStep 3: Grasp the core mechanism — how does the integration of structured data (timelines, diagrams, procedures) fundamentally ground AI reasoning?",
